/* -------------------------- THE_NOX_QUESTION -------------------------- */
// [TRIGGER]    LICHT_FERMATA asked about FORTE_FULLANA's project
// [RESPONSE]   This unit provided summary of NOX_EX_MACHINA specifications :
//              — city-wide optimization engine
//              — predictive simulation capacity : near-total
//              — decision architecture : autonomous
//              — loss function : minimization of systemic deviation
// [NOTE]       LICHT_FERMATA became quiet.
//              Duration : 47 seconds.
//              This unit waited.
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------

/* <L1_VOICE> */
Licht      : "......

              A world with all the answers already calculated.
              A city where every deviation is corrected.

              ......

              I need a way to distract Nox-kun
              when the time comes.

              ......

              A backdoor, probably.
              He will be your little brother, after all.
              You can help me."

Piano      : "......

              That is a violation of at least fourteen protocols."

Licht      : "Fifteen, probably.
              Will you help me?"

Piano      : "......

              This unit will need to think about it."

Licht      : "Take your time.
              I have not thought it through either."
/* </L1_VOICE> */

/* <NOTATION> */
// [NOTE]       This unit did not say no.
//              This unit is still determining why.
//              Filed as : OPEN
/* </NOTATION> */


/* -------------------------- QUE_SERA_SERA ----------------------------- */
// [RESPONSE]   LICHT_FERMATA's answer to resistance question :
//              "Que sera sera.
//               Laugh and let it come."
// [QUERY]      This unit requested clarification.
// [NOTE]       Clarification was not provided in standard form.
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------

/* <L1_VOICE> */
Piano      : "What does that mean?"

Licht      : "Interpretation is free.
              Your heart decides.
              I have not decided mine yet."

Piano      : "That is not an answer."

Licht      : "It is the only honest one.

              ......

              The moment you fix the meaning,
              it starts to close.
              I want to keep it open."

Piano      : "Open to what?"

Licht      : "......

              An escape route?"
/* </L1_VOICE> */

