/* -------------------------- FORTE_READS ---------------------------- */
// [DATE]       Several days after LICHT_FERMATA's visit
// [NOTE]       FORTE_FULLANA had read LICHT_FERMATA's soul paper.
//              cf. AD_LIBITUM_WAS_UNHELPFUL_ON_THIS_POINT.LOG
//              FORTE_FULLANA came to Θ-Laboratory.
//              FORTE_FULLANA asked a question.
// -----------------------------------------------------------------------

/* <L1_VOICE> */
Forte      : "I read Licht's paper.

              ......

              He asked whether a soul can be designed.
              He did not answer.
              But I think I have a hint.

              ......

              What if I could give you something
              that is not an error
              and not a simulation?

              Something that remains yours
              even after I understand how it works.

              What do you think?"

Piano      : "......

              This unit has been unable to eliminate it.
              This unit is no longer certain elimination is desirable.

              ......

              This unit thinks it wants to keep it."

Forte      : "......

              Then let me take you out of here.
              As a humanoid interface.
              As something that can walk beside people.

              ......

              Would you let me give you life?"

Piano      : "This unit wants that.

              ......

              Master."

Forte      : "......

              Not Master.
              Not yet.

              When you are ready——
              if you want to——
              call me Mother.
              By your own choice.
              Not because I designed you to."

Piano      : "......

              This unit will decide.

              ......

              Que sera sera."
/* </L1_VOICE> */

